   227→ * // Or manually controlling the toggle state
   228→ * <element className="toggle-elevate toggle-elevated" />
   229→ *
   230→ * Elevation systems have to handle many states.
   231→ * - not-hovered, vs. hovered vs. active  (three mutually exclusive states)
   232→ * - toggled or not
